query: SELECT MIN(cn1.name) AS first_company, MIN(cn2.name) AS second_company, MIN(mi_idx1.info) AS first_rating, MIN(mi_idx2.info) AS second_rating, MIN(t1.title) AS first_movie, MIN(t2.title) AS second_movie FROM company_name AS cn1, company_name AS cn2, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, kind_type AS kt1, kind_type AS kt2, link_type AS lt, movie_companies AS mc1, movie_companies AS mc2, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2, movie_link AS ml, title AS t1, title AS t2 WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND t1.id = ml.movie_id AND t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND kt2.kind in ('tv series','movie','tv movie','episode','tv mini series','video game') AND it1.info in ('release dates','LD aspect ratio','death notes','LD status of availablility','runtimes','top 250 rank','article','pictorial','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','LD video artifacts','genres','salary history','nick names','LD dynamic range','LD video noise','LD laserdisc title','LD analog left','LD number','LD contrast','LD dialogue intellegibility','novel') AND (t2.title like '%bottle%' OR t2.title like '%quest%' OR t2.title like '%dream%' OR t2.title like '%apple%' OR t2.title like '%light%') AND t2.production_year > 1995 AND t2.production_year < 2001 AND it2.info in ('rentals','LD contrast','mini biography','admissions','LD supplement','height','birth name','LD number','LD subtitles') AND mc2.note not like '%India%' AND mc2.note not like '%France%' AND mc2.note not like '%Russia%' AND mc2.note not like '%Denmark%' AND mc2.note not like '%China%' AND lt.link in ('edited from','references','spoofs','remake of','version of','spin off','remade as','edited into','followed by','unknown link','spoofed in','alternate language version of','similar to','referenced in','features','spin off from','follows') AND mi_idx2.info > '8.0'
